window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>A lethal orbital defense platform. A squad of green Marines. A silent alien killer. Who dies next? </b></p> <p>2441 AD. A quarantine platform in the Rakasa system goes quiet and a squad of freshly minted Marines are sent to investigate. The blood soon flows, but there is one Marine who has the bravery and cunning to take on even the most lethal hidden foe.&nbsp;</p> <p>Set 125 years before the events on Tranquility that sparked the creation of the Human Legion,<i> The Demons of Kor-Lir</i> is a standalone novella and introduction to the Sleeping Legion series.</p>"; 
